# Debian base-image (python:3.12-slim) OS-package CVEs with no upstream fix
# available as of 2026-07-05, in packages this app never invokes at runtime
# (perl-base, ncurses, gzip, libacl1 are baseline OS packages, not
# application dependencies). Evaluated switching to a different Debian
# release (bookworm) and to Alpine — bookworm has more unfixed findings,
# not fewer, and Alpine breaks the build (confluent-kafka's C extension has
# no musl-compatible wheel and needs a full build toolchain to compile from
# source). Re-evaluate this list when a patched package version ships.
CVE-2026-41992
CVE-2026-54369
CVE-2025-69720
CVE-2026-42496
CVE-2026-8376
CVE-2026-42497
CVE-2026-48962
